content.description: Starting with a right undercling and a gaston, power through the short, overhanging face to an easing finish. In the DL Bouldering Guide as a V5 from a higher start.  The true sit start is still an undone project as of now.Come up through the boulder field, passing Block Party and the Bully Pulpit to Battle Wound. This is in the trees to the left, below Night Grinder.Lat: 43.41400, Lon: -89.72356You could also approach by traversing along the top of the boulder field from Balanced Rock Wall, and passing through the band of trees.
content.location: Just below night grinder. Left of Battle wound. DL Bouldering guide has a good map/directions to area.

content.description: Another boulder lurking in the trees, just off the boulder field.
